How to configure? Please follow this prcedure:
1. /etc/environment
1)add emulator and node bin to PATH
/home/ubuntu/android-sdk-linux/tools
/home/ubuntu/node/bin

2)add GOPATH
/home/ubuntu/node

2. /etc/rc.local
start node automatically when instance booting
su ubuntu - -c /home/ubuntu/node/bin/node

